```R
> cor(x, x+1)
[1] 1
> cor(x, -x)
[1] -1
> cor(x, 0.5*x)
[1] 1
> 0.5*x
 [1]  6.0  8.5 25.0 16.5 49.0 38.5 19.5 39.5  3.5 13.0
> cor(x, 0.5*x+1)
[1] 1
> cor(x, -0.5*x+1)
[1] -1
> y=sample(1:100, 10)
> y
 [1] 53 69 57 93 27 37 60 83 77 55
> 
> cor(x,y)
[1] -0.4683468
